This paper focuses on the impact of refactoring on software libraries, which is a common practice in software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the impact of API changes on client users, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software design (cs.SD). The study uses a tool-based approach to analyze a large-scale dataset, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
